809.excerpt:
GIF IT UP 2015 entry from Kathy Onarheim in Pewaukee, Wisconsin. Source material courtesy The National Gallery of Art (Washington, D.C.) via DPLA. Kathy writes: 

The art files were mesmerizing. I found this one and the serious figures seemed to speak fun behind them. It also gave me the opportunity to expand my skills and take on new challenges.
